name: Gweda Artstyle
description:
This LORA was made to emulate the art style of Gweda. Please check out the original artist:

https://twitter.com/gweda8593

https://www.patreon.com/gweda

https://www.pixiv.net/en/users/17282018

https://gweda.fanbox.cc

This is the first LORA I've ever made for an art style, so please let me know if you encounter any problems.

I am using AbyssOrangeMix3 (AOM3)

I don't know how well it works with other models.

It is very NFSW as it has been trained exclusively on NSFW images, but it is still able to generate clothed art, but you may want to add "motion lines" to negative prompts.

It can replicate multiple sex positions relatively consistently, some better than others. Just look at the sample images for prompt ideas.

Some images have been created using additional character LORAs. All LORAs used can be found in my profile.

A weight between 0.8-1.0 is recommended.
